OL,3,CThieves target two Peeblesshire hotels
OL,4,Con same night
OL,6,FTwo men made off with four figure sums
OL,7,Fof money from one hotel in Peebles and
OL,8,Fanother in Innerleithen.
OL,10,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,11,Fafter two break-ins and thefts in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of Friday morning.
OL,14,FAt around 1.20am, on Friday 2nd
OL,15,FJanuary, two men entered the Park
OL,16,FHotel on Innerleithen Road in Peebles
OL,17,Fand stole a four-figure sum of cash
OL,18,Fbefore making off in the direction of
OL,19,FHigh Street.
