OL,4,Con same night
OL,6,FThen, at around 2.15am, the same men
OL,7,Fbroke into the Traquair Arms Hotel on
OL,8,FTraquair Road in Innerleithen, where
OL,9,Fthey stole a safe as well as a four-
OL,10,Ffigure sum of cash.
OL,12,FThe incidents are being treated as
OL,13,Flinked.
OL,15,FBoth men are described as white, in
OL,16,Ftheir 60s, and wore dark clothing and
OL,17,Fgloves. One wore a cap and the other a
OL,18,Fbeanie style hat.
