OL,6,FDetective Constable Nicky Batten said:
OL,7,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to identify
OL,8,Fthe two men involved and trace the car
OL,9,Fthey used. Officers are studying CCTV
OL,10,Ffrom in and around the area to gather
OL,11,Fmore information.
OL,13,F"I would urge anyone who was in these
OL,14,Fareas early on Friday morning who has
OL,15,Fany information or personal footage
OL,16,Fwhich could assist our enquiries to
OL,17,Fplease contact us."
